# ECC Mobile App — Environment Variables Template
#
# Copy ke `.env` (untuk lokal default), `.env.development`, atau `.env.production`
# sesuai kebutuhan. File aktualnya gitignored.
#
# Reference: docs/production-launch-brief-2026-05-23.md

# === API base URL ===
# Highest priority. Override app.json extra.apiBaseUrl.
# Untuk EAS build, set di eas.json `env` block per profile — file ini hanya
# dipakai oleh `npx expo start` lokal.

# Production (default):
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.eccchurch.global

# Local backend dev (uncomment + sesuaikan IP Mac):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.10:4100

# Staging (kalau BE provision):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://staging-api.eccchurch.global

# === Error reporting ===
# Tidak pakai third-party — errors push ke BE endpoint /diagnostics/error.
# Lihat src/services/errorReporting.ts + docs/backend-request-diagnostics-error-endpoint.md
# Zero env vars needed.
